// Inter-city flight routes — drives the airport ticket office's destination
// list. Each `hub` is one airport with its building rect (sourced from the
// matching world-map place), the in-world ticket counter the player walks up
// to, and the arrival tile fly-ins land on.
//
// `placeId` references data/world-map.json5; ecs/spawn.ts spawnAirports reads
// the place rect for the building footprint, so moving the airport on the
// world map (its world-map entry) automatically moves the spawned building.
//
// `sceneId` says which scene this airport lives in (see src/ecs/world.ts
// SceneId). Each scene is its own koota world; flying from one hub to
// another always crosses between two scenes — the flight midpoint swaps
// the active scene to the destination's `sceneId` and respawns the player
// at `arrivalTile`. Even hypothetical same-scene routes go through the
// scene-swap codepath (it's a no-op when from.sceneId === to.sceneId).
//
// `counterTile` is the tile-space position of the ticket counter Interactable
// — clicking it opens the FlightModal listing routes whose `from` matches
// this hub. `arrivalTile` is where the player teleports after fading out at
// the previous airport (one tile outside the door, on the street, so they
// don't immediately re-trigger the click).
//
// `routes` are directed edges: `{ from, to, durationMin, fare }`. Adding a
// new destination = add a hub here and add routes from/to it. The UI is
// fully data-driven — no other plumbing required.

{
  hubs: [
    {
      id: 'startTownAirport',
      nameZh: '冯·布劳恩航天港',
      placeId: 'startTownAirport',
      sceneId: 'startTown',
      counterTile: { x: 20, y: 38 },
      arrivalTile: { x: 20, y: 31 },
      description: '冯·布劳恩中心区南郊的航天港售票处。',
    },
    {
      id: 'zumCityAirport',
      nameZh: '祖姆市航天港',
      placeId: 'zumCityAirport',
      sceneId: 'zumCity',
      counterTile: { x: 150, y: 149 },
      arrivalTile: { x: 150, y: 142 },
      description: 'Side 3 共和国首府的中央航天港售票处。',
    },
  ],

  // Round-trip pair: 6 game-hours (360 min) each way, ¥800 fare. Symmetrical
  // for now — pricing/duration can diverge later (premium one-way, faster
  // courier flights, etc.).
  routes: [
    {
      from: 'startTownAirport',
      to: 'zumCityAirport',
      durationMin: 360,
      fare: 800,
    },
    {
      from: 'zumCityAirport',
      to: 'startTownAirport',
      durationMin: 360,
      fare: 800,
    },
  ],
}
